": "codex"}, "auto_retried": 2, "force_fallback": true, "force_started": "2026-07-07T11:30:00-04:00"}, "7": {"step": "done", "tasks": {"availability": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T07:41:24-04:00", "models": {"claude": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:41:20-04:00"}, "codex": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:41:24-04:00"}}}, "draft_glm": {"state": "skipped", "updated": "2026-07-07T07:41:24-04:00", "model": "", "reason": "未選用（單稿模式）"}, "segment": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-06T23:31:43-04:00", "model": "claude"}, "skeleton": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-06T23:31:43-04:00"}, "draft_codex": {"state": "done", "section": 26, "updated": "2026-07-07T07:45:06-04:00", "model": "codex", "sections_total": 26, "reason": "codex unavailable during draft_codex: ers path=/Users/davidshih/.codex/.tmp/plugins/plugins/ngs-analysis/.codex-plugin/plugin.json\ncodex\n<<<TRANSLATION\n論中問：這是在哪裡說的？答：是在契經中說的。就像契經中說有四種作為緣的性質（四緣性）：因緣性、等無間緣性、所緣緣性、增上緣性。這裡的「性」，意思是緣的種類。在六因之中，除去能作因，其餘五因就是因緣性。除了阿羅漢臨近涅槃……\n>>>\n<<<NOTE\n原文至「除阿羅漢臨涅」即中斷，應是下文「臨涅槃時」的開頭，故譯文保留未完句。\n>>>\n2026-07-07T03:32:28"}, "review": {"state": "done", "section": 26, "updated": "2026-07-07T08:00:10-04:00", "model": "claude", "sections_total": 26}, "checks": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:00:10-04:00"}, "html": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:00:10-04:00"}, "commit": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:00:11-04:00"}}, "availability": {"claude": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:41:20-04:00"}, "codex": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:41:24-04:00"}}, "models": {"segment": "claude", "draft_codex": "codex", "merge": "claude", "repair": "claude"}, "auto_retried": 1, "force_started": "2026-07-07T11:30:00-04:00"}, "8": {"step": "done", "tasks": {"availability": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T07:55:38-04:00", "models": {"claude": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:55:35-04:00"}, "codex": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:55:38-04:00"}}}, "draft_glm": {"state": "skipped", "updated": "2026-07-07T07:55:38-04:00", "model": "", "reason": "未選用（單稿模式）"}, "segment": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-06T23:48:11-04:00", "model": "claude"}, "skeleton": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-06T23:48:11-04:00"}, "draft_codex": {"state": "done", "section": 20, "updated": "2026-07-07T07:59:34-04:00", "model": "codex", "sections_total": 20, "reason": "codex unavailable during draft_codex: ，又怎麼會緣著大梵而仍然生起戒禁取呢？\n\n又有其他論師說：是在中有之中見過。\n\n問：他們住在中有之中，並沒有長時間停留的道理，因為對受生沒有障礙。那麼梵眾怎麼可以說：「我們曾見過這樣一位有情，壽命長久、久住世間」呢？\n\n所以應當說：梵眾就是住在自己的天處，憶念此生先前所經歷的事；也就是說，他們先前曾見大梵長壽久住，後來再次見到時，便生起這樣的念頭。\n\n有色身的有情，身體同一而想不同（身一想異），如極光淨天，\n>>>\n<<<NOTE\n「身異想一」中，梵眾與大梵同起「梵眾由大梵所生」這一類想，故名想一；但大梵身量、容貌、威德等皆異於梵眾，故名身異。\n>>>\n2026-07-07T03:52:20."}, "review": {"state": "done", "section": 20, "updated": "2026-07-07T08:09:48-04:00", "model": "codex", "sections_total": 20, "model_events": [{"stage": "merge", "from": "claude", "to": "codex", "reason": "You've hit your session limit · resets 12:20pm (America/New_York)", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:01:31-04:00"}]}, "checks": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:09:48-04:00"}, "html": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:09:48-04:00"}, "commit": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:09:50-04:00"}}, "availability": {"claude": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:55:35-04:00"}, "codex": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T07:55:38-04:00"}}, "models": {"segment": "claude", "draft_codex": "codex", "merge": "codex", "repair": "claude"}, "auto_retried": 1, "force_started": "2026-07-07T11:30:00-04:00", "model_events": [{"stage": "merge", "from": "claude", "to": "codex", "reason": "You've hit your session limit · resets 12:20pm (America/New_York)", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:01:31-04:00"}]}, "9": {"step": "done", "tasks": {"availability": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:00:20-04:00", "models": {"claude": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T08:00:15-04:00"}, "codex": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T08:00:20-04:00"}}}, "draft_glm": {"state": "skipped", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:00:20-04:00", "model": "", "reason": "未選用（單稿模式）"}, "segment": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-06T23:51:07-04:00", "model": "claude"}, "skeleton": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-06T23:51:07-04:00"}, "draft_codex": {"state": "done", "section": 24, "updated": "2026-07-07T08:05:02-04:00", "model": "codex", "sections_total": 24, "reason": "codex unavailable during draft_codex: ，也如同中有不可被看見一樣，也不可被觸到，因為中有身極為微細，所以這個詰難不合理。各趣中有雖然同在一腹之中，也不會彼此觸碰、焚燒，因為各自的業力有所遮止。\n\n欲界中有的身量，雖然如同五、六歲的小兒，但諸根明利。菩薩的中有，則如壯盛年時，身形圓滿，具足各種相好；所以住於中有、將要入胎時，能照耀百俱胝四大洲等世界。\n\n若是這樣，為什麼菩薩母在夢中見到白象子來入自己的右脇呢？\n\n答：這是吉祥瑞相，並不關涉中有本身。因為菩薩早已久遠捨離傍生趣的緣故，如訖栗……\n>>>\n<<<NOTE\n原文結尾「如訖栗」句未完，應屬下段續文，故此處依現有文字保留未竟語勢。\n>>>\n2026-07-07T03:51:46"}, "review": {"state": "done", "section": 24, "updated": "2026-07-07T12:21:04-04:00", "model": "codex", "sections_total": 24, "model_events": [{"stage": "merge", "from": "claude", "to": "codex", "reason": "You've hit your session limit · resets 12:20pm (America/New_York)", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:05:04-04:00"}]}, "checks": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T12:21:04-04:00"}, "html": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T12:21:04-04:00"}, "commit": {"state": "done", "updated": "2026-07-07T12:21:06-04:00"}}, "availability": {"claude": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T08:00:15-04:00"}, "codex": {"state": "available", "checked": "2026-07-07T08:00:20-04:00"}}, "models": {"segment": "claude", "draft_codex": "codex", "merge": "codex", "repair": "claude"}, "auto_retried": 1, "force_started": "2026-07-07T11:30:00-04:00", "model_events": [{"stage": "merge", "from": "claude", "to": "codex", "reason": "You've hit your session limit · resets 12:20pm (America/New_York)", "updated": "2026-07-07T08:05:04-04:00"}]}, "10": {"step": "done", "tasks": {"availability": {"state": "done", "updated": "20